snippet.title: AFTER-H | FREE TO PLAY - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
AFTER-H is taking off September 23rd, 2019!

Join the Martian battlefields and fight in a competitive VR FPS.

PLAY for FREE:
- Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/854110/AFTERH/
- Viveport : coming soon

Join the fight on http://www.after-h.com

Let's keep in touch!
https://twitter.com/afterhvr
https://facebook.com/afterHVR/
https://www.instagram.com/afterhvr/
https://discord.gg/k9YefU6
